{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot be sure whether it was six or seven days, and we were shipped out to Skarzysko-Kamienna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Skarzysko-Kamienna was a munitions factory of the Hassock enterprise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hassock was the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It had three divisions, A, B, and C.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were in division A.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Division C was a chemical division, where they mixed the chemicals needed for explosives for the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had an explosive that they called [NON-ENGLISH]-- [NON-ENGLISH] was the name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was severely hepatotoxic, and people who-- not only did the [NON-ENGLISH] look yellow in itself, the chemical, but the people, because of hepatotoxicity, turned jaundice, so they became as yellow as a chemical and died.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No precautions, of course, were taken, like masks to prevent inhalation, and so, to the people who worked there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They-- most of them actually were women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They inhaled it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had no protection whatever, and they succumbed to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But those who died were as yellow as the [NON-ENGLISH] itself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, amongst the people who worked in-- in-- in-- in that division C was Ida, my cousin, that is now in Toronto that I mentioned earlier.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "By-- by a miracle, she was not put into contact with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She met up with us at a-- with a strange coincidence, when she went to-- to be showered and-- and [NON-ENGLISH], the way they called it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We, of course-- we were delighted that she is still alive, and we were-- we were never losing hope of survival.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And indeed, as it happened, all three of us survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father and I, we were working on the railroad again, loading and unloading.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They called it transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But my father had an unusual thing that-- he became an assistant to the driver of the locomotive.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
